{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_13_level_main_13-14_end","storyGroup":"main_13","storySort":163,"storyDependence":"main_13_level_main_13-14_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"13-16","storyName":"“我们”","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"九找到了Guard留下的录音，并真正决定了整合运动应该为之奋战的目标，她流放了杀死无辜萨卡兹感染者的维多利亚感染者，并告别了Guard。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_13-14_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_13-14","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":19,"next":21,"characters":["九","绝望的难民","珀茜瓦尔","诺威尔","慌乱的难民","紧张的感染者","塔露拉","雷德"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":7},{"type":"charslot","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"interlude","maskid":"ui_cutin_mask_horizon","style":"1","size":"1500, 420","offset":"20,0","channel":"2","id":11},{"type":"2","channel":"2","name":"bg_lungmen_n","afrom":"0","ato":"1","aduration":"3","sfrom":"1.6,1.6","sto":"1.6,1.6","sduration":"0","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"2","channel":"2","name":"bg_lungmen_n","pfrom":"0,0","pto":"-80,0","duration":"30","block":"false","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":14},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"sticker","id":16,"multi":"true","text":"我还在龙门近卫局的时候，有时会抽上一个下午的时间，在那座城市中穿行。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":17,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我深知我的职责要求我对抗什么。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":18,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们以秩序作为自己的武器，约束混乱，惩戒纷争，打击犯罪，纠正错误。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":19},{"type":"sticker","id":20,"multi":"true","text":"在那时，我总是会想，人们......太容易腐坏了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":21,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们出生的时候总是纯洁无瑕，但随着年龄的增长，那些恶就如同霉变，侵蚀每一缕枝叶。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":22},{"type":"1","channel":"2","slot":"m","offset":"-170,50","name":"cutin_char_15","sfrom":"1,1","sto":"1,1","aduration":"2","block":"false","id":23},{"type":"1","channel":"2","slot":"m","pfrom":"-170,50","pto":"-120,50","duration":"40","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":25},{"type":"sticker","id":26,"multi":"true","text":"曾经我以为，如果我们足够强大，足够无私，这片大地上就不再会有罪恶。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":27,"multi":"true","text":"\\n直到我成为了感染者，直到我来到了龙门的贫民区。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":28,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我才真正地体会到，“公正”这个词，比人更加羸弱。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":29},{"type":"sticker","id":30,"multi":"true","text":"污秽的土壤长出了变异的植物，温室中的花草有资格指责它们的扭曲吗？有权力剪去它们的枝蔓吗？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":31,"multi":"true","text":"\\n未曾共享同一种土壤，就无从谈论同一种公正。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":32},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"4","id":34},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":35},{"type":"interlude","channel":"2","clear":"true","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":37},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_bg_43_g11_breweryinforest_b.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":38},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tense_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_tense_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":39,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0.5","id":40},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_labber","id":43},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_statuecollapse","volume":"0.9","delay":"0.5","id":45},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":47},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_riot","volume":"0.9","delay":"0.5","id":48},{"type":"delay","time":"5","id":49},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":51},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"快点，让所有人往外撤，尽量远离建筑！","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绝望的难民","text":"我的东西还在里面！我全部的家当！","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"什么东西？","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绝望的难民","text":"枕头......和褥子！是我从家里带出来的最后的东西了！","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":60},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"别发疯！跟我去后面避难！","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你还没感染吧？那就珍惜你的好运气！","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"人群太混乱了，逃出来的人不少，感染者和非感染者混杂，可能还有些亡命徒。我们不知道原先藏在这里的人都是什么来路。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"这场火......这里离战场并不远，我们不知道这里的火光会引来谁的注意。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我们可以直接离开！我们对这场火灾不负有责任！","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4d/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"九！做决定！","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4d/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":73},{"type":"dialog","id":74},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"sticker","id":77,"multi":"true","text":"尖叫，哭声，倒在泥地里又重新爬起来的人。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":78,"multi":"true","text":"\\n火光在他们的背后，烧得透红。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":79},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"是......是感染者点的火！就是因为，有个感染者炸了，酒厂才会——","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_329_1$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的感染者","text":"跟我们有什么关系！","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_329_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_329_1$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的感染者","text":"那个萨卡兹，难道不是你们引来的吗？","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_329_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"我们没有！","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"都怪你们这些感染者！要不是因为你们，我们本来能在这里藏得更久的！","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_329_1$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的感染者","text":"*维多利亚粗口*，你说什么？","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_329_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_329_1$1","focus":"m","id":93},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":94},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的感染者","text":"别忘了是谁收留了你们！","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_329_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":97},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你居然敢打我？！","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你——","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"行了！","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":104},{"type":"dialog","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"sticker","id":108,"multi":"true","text":"无休无止的相互指责。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":109,"multi":"true","text":"\\n永不停息的相互辱骂。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":110},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"如果你不想走，我可以把你送回火里。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"整......整合运动，你们和梅斯一伙的！","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"要不是感染者，要不是感染者......","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"要不是感染者，怎样？","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"睁眼看看，不是感染者把你害成这样，不是感染者让你只能缩在个废弃的酒厂里，不是感染者让你一无所有。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"除了身上没长石头，你和我们没有区别。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们因为疾病被夺走了一切，你呢？你甚至未经历我们之难，却落得一样田地。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"呵。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你——你又知道什么？！","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你被流水线上的机器咬掉过手指吗？你被扔出过工厂大门吗？你被领主烧掉过房子吗？","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你们嚎叫自己遭到的不公，遭遇不公的又不只是你们！","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"那个烧我房子的子爵，所有人都说他儿子其实有矿石病，那又怎样！他是大人物，他可以把儿子送去哥伦比亚，住高档医院！","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"我们呢？我呢？就因为我交不出税款，还顶撞了他，他就能烧我的房子，烧死我两个孩子！","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"没人敢管他，他是领主，而我是残疾的穷光蛋！","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"你们不是唯一被奴役的人，凭什么只有你们，好像能光明正大地站起来，杀了那些欺负人的人！","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"凭什么？因为我们不愿意继续被奴役。","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"也没人告诉过你，你不可以反抗。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"我......我——","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慌乱的难民","text":"我......我没办法，我没有你们那些源石技艺。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"别给自己找借口，不是每个感染者都有厉害的源石技艺。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"九，我们已经在整队了，要撤离吗？","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......告诉雷德，带几队人，严密监视周围的情况。既然战线胶着，战争的几方就不一定还能抽调出人手，去检查一场远方的大火。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"珀茜瓦尔，安抚这些逃出来的人，组织医疗、检查和登记，保险起见，我们最多在这里耽搁一天。","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我知道了！","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"......","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我会帮忙，我熟悉烧伤和呼吸道呛入粉尘的处理。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"还有，我们还是联系不上Guard！","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我们不确定他有没有出来！","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......放心，我会找到他。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们可是从切尔诺伯格出来的。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"九，源石粉尘的浓度——","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"sticker","id":180,"multi":"true","text":"我已冲向燃烧着的酒厂。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":181,"multi":"true","text":"\\n在龙门，我曾不止一次走入相似的火场。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":182,"multi":"true","text":"\\n以近卫局警员的身份，以贫民区住客的身份。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":183},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"dialog","id":185},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":186},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":187},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":188},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":189},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_bg_bg_lungmen_b.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":190},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":192},{"type":"charslot","id":193},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":195},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":196},{"type":"sticker","id":197,"multi":"true","text":"火灾，意味着失去，意味着破灭。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":198,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我总能看到在烧焦的残骸前哭泣的人们。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":199,"multi":"true","text":"\\n有时候是感染者，有时候，只是普通的住户。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":200},{"type":"sticker","id":201,"multi":"true","text":"这时候，就会有流言在围观的人群中蔓延。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":202,"multi":"true","text":"\\n烧死了几个感染者，烧死了几个普通人。这是感染者要报复欺辱他的街坊，这是邻居们受不了躲了满楼的病人。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":203,"multi":"true","text":"\\n可是，从没有人问起，为什么，上城区的火灾总是能在第一时间扑灭。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":204,"multi":"true","text":"\\n而毁去数栋楼的大火，弄不清楚死了多少人的大火，总是发生在贫民区。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"dialog","id":207},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":209},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_bg_43_g11_breweryinforest_b.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":210},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":212},{"type":"charslot","id":213},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"sticker","id":217,"multi":"true","text":"我冲进了酒厂的大门，离出口不远的地方，能看到一场猛烈的崩塌。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":218,"multi":"true","text":"\\n有只伸在金属与瓦砾之外的手。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":219,"multi":"true","text":"\\n握着的，是Guard的录音机。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":220},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":221},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":223},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":224},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1d/Avg_bg_bg_coldforest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":226},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":228},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":229,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","id":230},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"sticker","id":234,"multi":"true","text":"“或者说......我们所团结的人，我们希望与之并肩披荆斩棘的人——”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":235,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“只有感染者吗？”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":236,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“只有......他们吗？”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":237},{"type":"sticker","id":238,"multi":"true","text":"“感染者......总会成为一切跌落的终点......我们因为相同的遭遇而聚在一起。”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":239,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“但，让我们并肩作战的......不只是疾病。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":240},{"type":"sticker","id":241,"multi":"true","text":"“如果我们遇到了一位......贵族，他用手中的权力盘剥他人，我们会怎么看待他？”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":242,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“如果......他其实是个感染者呢？”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":243},{"type":"sticker","id":244,"multi":"true","text":"“我们不能仅以感染与否为......唯一的准绳，唯一的口号。”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":245,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“我们身边的伙伴，必须要有相同的信念......不只是报复那些曾受的欺辱，还有，带给苦我们之苦的人，解放。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":246,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“这片大地上的被奴役者不只有我们......我们该与他们站在一起。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":247,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“我们必须要让他们与我们......站在一起。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":248,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“我们......不能只对抗疾病。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":249},{"type":"sticker","id":250,"multi":"true","text":"“我们该对抗的，究竟是什么？”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":251,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“我们要建立的......又是什么？”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":252,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“我——”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":253},{"type":"sticker","id":254,"multi":"true","text":"*沙沙声*","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":255},{"type":"sticker","id":256,"multi":"true","text":"“很多年前，刚感染的时候，我很......爱喝酒。那时候，Ace队长警告我，再这么......下去，我早晚死在酒上。”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":257,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“......哈哈。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":258,"multi":"true","text":"\\n“这里......确实是个酿酒厂。”","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":259},{"type":"sticker","id":260,"multi":"true","text":"“——”","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":264},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"九，你已经听了很多遍了。","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我知道。","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"塔露拉......我在想，如果我们真的建立了一座感染者的城市，它会是什么样子？","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"它真的不是个......临终关怀中心而已吗？","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们只是在那座城市里，等待着崩解后的源石粉尘覆盖一切，等待着一场又一场的死亡。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"是啊。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们......不能只是在结局等待。","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"charslot","id":284},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":285},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"九，塔露拉。","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"怎么了？","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我想......我会暂时离开你们的队伍。昨天，我在难民中遇到了几个从伦蒂尼姆逃出来的人。","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"他们提到了一些......我很在意的事情，那里也许藏着我一直在寻找的人。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我将动身前往伦蒂尼姆。","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"伦蒂尼姆，那里很危险。","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我想，塔露拉应该告诉过你我的身份。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"“长生者”。","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"是啊，我无法死去。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我已经......越来越无法忍受这个事实。","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......你想杀死你自己？","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你是怎么，获得“长生”的？","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"......“长生”，呵。","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"起初，我怎么会意识到命运和我开了一个怎样的玩笑？","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我也曾有过一段幸福的时日。","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我结识了我的唯一一位妻子，有了孩子和家庭，我一心扑在关于源石技艺的研究上......当然，主要是研究自己。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"孩子长大，我们变老，这一切顺应天理。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"直到我的妻子死于意外，随后是战火纷飞，我被迫离开了孩子。逃难的那些年，我突然发现，自己几乎没有变化。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"帝皇们掀起战争，过些年，国王又被吊死，公爵们的阴谋浮上台面。然后，是萨卡兹......","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我都不再变化，直到今天。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我每天都在做噩梦，梦里，有个我不认识的声音......或者是我认识的所有声音，都在对我呼唤。","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"“痛苦使你永生，唯有幸福才能将你杀死。”","id":329,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"我其实早就意识到了，可我怎么才能感到幸福和释然？","id":331,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"在目睹了一场又一场死亡，在经历了一次又一次悲剧之后，我怎么才能感到幸福和释然？","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"既然，这是个属于痛苦与绝望的时代......那么，我就找出那些躲藏在时代背后的人。","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我无权挽留你。","id":339,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"但也不必急着道别，你想回到战争的中心......那我们未必殊途。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"是吗？我以为你们组织了足够的成员，就会回哥伦比亚......","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/cd/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"再逃到一个地方，只会没完没了。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"......也对。也许我们要对抗的本就是同一种东西。","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1066_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺威尔","text":"也替我......为Guard献一束花。","id":349,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_1066_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我会的。","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":353},{"type":"charslot","id":354},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"九......","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"珀茜瓦尔，你......","id":360,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我没事！我眼睛......只是被烟熏的。","id":362,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"第三批过来的感染者们已经登记好了，七个人，他们都是曾经在这个作坊领过药的人。","id":364,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"听他们说，因为这个作坊，附近这片森林曾经聚集了挺多感染者的小村庄。","id":366,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"后来，作坊被毁了，大部分人走了，或者死了......但还有些人留在附近。","id":368,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"他们都被这场大火引来了。","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"是啊，他们都被这场大火引来了。","id":372,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":373},{"type":"dialog","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"sticker","id":377,"multi":"true","text":"我看着眼前的花瓣，是那个叫梅斯的人给我的。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":378,"multi":"true","text":"\\n这里的整合运动医生为这些草药耗费了一生的时间，听她说，Guard也为了它们而死。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":379,"multi":"true","text":"\\n其中大多数的植物我都认识，在现代的制药企业诞生之前，感染者们就靠咀嚼它们来缓解痛苦。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":380,"multi":"true","text":"\\n也许，有了这些做参考，我们粗劣的药物，能变得稍微更有效一点点。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":381},{"type":"sticker","id":382,"multi":"true","text":"我们不能只是在结局，等着那些跌落的人。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":383,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们要做的，也不只是这些。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":384},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"Guard......我们的讨论还没像样的结果，接下来，得靠我自作主张了。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"那个，九。","id":389,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我们想为Guard办一场小小的告别仪式，耽误不了多少时间。","id":391,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"嗯。","id":393,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我会让这里，开出花来。","id":395,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":396},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"dialog","id":398},{"type":"charslot","id":399},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":401},{"type":"charslot","id":402},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"sticker","id":406,"multi":"true","text":"那场大火烧了一夜。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":407,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们最终放弃了救出Guard的遗体。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":408},{"type":"sticker","id":409,"multi":"true","text":"雷德找了一棵茁壮的树，笔直，漂亮，直指天空。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":410,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他挖了个坑，把Guard的那条可爱的毛巾埋了进去。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":411,"multi":"true","text":"\\n花朵在刚被掘开的土壤周围生长了起来。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":412,"multi":"true","text":"\\n那条毛巾上的碎花太粗劣，这样的花圃，才与他更相称。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":413},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":414},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"......","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"讯问结束了，我问了每个从作坊里出来的人。","id":418,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"那个死在地下仓库里的萨卡兹......开摩托车的家伙。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"他被人蓄意杀死，凶手是——几个维多利亚的感染者。","id":422,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"他们被萨卡兹逐出了家，有的还失去了亲人，他们义愤填膺，我，呃，让他们冷静了点。","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"怎么做？","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"在乌萨斯的时候，整合运动与那些纠察队、税官和矿场守卫战斗，所有人曾以为，那就是团结。","id":430,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"不是的，那只是因为别无选择，我们需要折断抵在我们喉间的刀。","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"整合运动曾因仇恨而行动，仇恨的目标，却越来越模糊而宽泛。","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"感染者没有祖国......没有身份，没有血统，这不能再只是一句有煽动性的口号。","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们需要的是更明确的准则，需要的是更精准的纲领。","id":438,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"Guard......和我讨论过这些。","id":440,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他说，若沉湎于地位与权术之人是感染者，我们弃他们于不顾。只因他们仍旧享受盘剥的权力，将疾病视作工具。","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他说，若受压迫者中，并非只有患病的同胞，我们则给予他们相同的解放。只因他们足以与我们并肩作战，反抗需要更多力量。","id":444,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......切尔诺伯格的教训已经够大了。","id":446,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"......他总是想这么多。我还以为......","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"我还以为他真的能带着我们干些大事。","id":450,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他会的，哪怕他死了。死在他还微不足道，遭人唾弃的时刻。","id":452,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"那些凶手？","id":454,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"无端宣泄暴力的人不能加入我们。纵使作为维多利亚人，是这场仗把他们变成了这样。","id":456,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"但要是纵容了这一次呢......我们的队伍里会发生什么？","id":458,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"乌萨斯人，哥伦比亚人，维多利亚人，莱塔尼亚人。菲林，佩洛，黎博利，卡普里尼，萨卡兹。","id":460,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"力量该清晰指向共同的目标，而不是成为怨恨与裂痕，给别人从内部瓦解我们的机会。","id":462,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"博卓卡斯替和乌萨斯，应该教会过我们这一点。","id":464,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":466,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他们会被流放。","id":468,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他们的去路，必须自己选。","id":470,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"整合运动说到做到。","id":472,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":473},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"......我明白了。","id":474,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"我会向所有人转述你刚才说的，还有，那些凶手......我会处理。","id":476,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":477},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":478},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":479},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":480},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":482,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......塔露拉。我曾认识一位感染者，她拥有煊赫的血统，显贵的头衔。","id":484,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"但她放弃了这些，因为她说，她求索的是“公平”。","id":486,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你认识她。","id":488,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"m","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":490,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"哪怕在这里的很多人，也听说过你的想法，整合运动最早的愿景，被夸大、被误传以后的愿景。","id":492,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"但我们要的不是一座感染者的移动城市。","id":494,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们要的是，让所有王公贵族，让所有高高在上的欺辱者，让所有试图分化我们，打压我们，消灭我们的人知道——","id":496,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"他们所蔑视的锋刃正高悬头顶。","id":498,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"告别......已经结束了，这不是第一场告别，也不会是最后一场。","id":500,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"走吧，我们在维多利亚的工作还没有结束。","id":502,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":503},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":504},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":505},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":506},{"type":"character","id":507},{"type":"image","id":508}],"characters":["九","绝望的难民","珀茜瓦尔","诺威尔","慌乱的难民","紧张的感染者","塔露拉","雷德"]}